column4:
youdaotrans
这份报告有效地提升了全国性讨论中对社交媒体长期以来的担忧。与此同时，许多州和联邦议员都在社交媒体几乎不存在或根本不存在的时代长大，他们一直在为如何限制社交媒体的使用而苦苦挣扎。
baidu
这份报告有效地提升了全国对话中对社交媒体酝酿已久的担忧，与此同时，州和联邦立法者一直在努力限制社交媒体的使用，其中许多人是在社交媒体几乎不存在或根本不存在的时代提出的。
column5: The report, effectively elevating long-simmering concerns around social media in the national conversation, came as state and federal lawmakers, many of them raised in an era when social media barely existed or didn’t exist at all, have been struggling with how to set limits on its use.
column6: The report, effectively elevating {{c1::long-simmering}} concerns around social media in the national conversation, came as state and federal lawmakers, many of them raised in an era when social media barely existed or didn’t exist at all, have been struggling with how to set limits on its use.
